RAZGOVOR

4
00:03:01,205 --> 00:03:03,435
Imam sastanak sa g. Ullmanom.

5
00:03:03,685 --> 00:03:05,437
Zovem se Jack Torrance.

6
00:03:05,685 --> 00:03:08,120
Njegova kancelarija je prva vrata levo.

7
00:03:08,366 --> 00:03:09,481
Hvala.

8
00:03:26,128 --> 00:03:26,924
G. Ullman?

9
00:03:27,169 --> 00:03:28,318
Jack Torrance.

10
00:03:28,569 --> 00:03:30,446
Uite, Jack.

11
00:03:31,529 --> 00:03:33,885
- Drago mi je.
- I meni takoer.

12
00:03:34,130 --> 00:03:35,609
Moja sekretarica, Susie.

13
00:03:36,010 --> 00:03:38,365
- Drago mi je.
- Lako ste nas nali?

14
00:03:38,610 --> 00:03:41,250
Bez problema.
Vozio sam tri i po sata.

15
00:03:41,491 --> 00:03:43,322
Odlino vreme.

16
00:03:43,691 --> 00:03:45,170
Sedite, Jack.

17
00:03:45,411 --> 00:03:47,084
Oseajte se kao
kod svoje kue.

18
00:03:47,332 --> 00:03:48,481
elite li kafu?

19
00:03:48,732 --> 00:03:51,087
Ako ete i vi,
vrlo rado. Hvala.

20
00:03:51,332 --> 00:03:52,208
- Susie.
- Odmah.

21
00:03:52,452 --> 00:03:54,045
Pozovite Billa Wotsona.

22
00:03:54,293 --> 00:03:55,726
Dobro.

23
00:04:06,095 --> 00:04:07,210
Mama?

24
00:04:08,015 --> 00:04:09,130
Da?

25
00:04:09,535 --> 00:04:13,006
Stvarno eli provesti zimu
u tom hotelu?

26
00:04:13,616 --> 00:04:14,844
Naravno.

27
00:04:15,096 --> 00:04:16,973
Bie zabavno.

28
00:04:18,777 --> 00:04:20,768
Da. Verovatno.

29
00:04:21,017 --> 00:04:25,011
Ovde se ionako
nemam s kim igrati.

30
00:04:25,738 --> 00:04:29,128
Znam. Treba vremena
za nalaenje novih prijatelja.

31
00:04:30,618 --> 00:04:32,814
Da. Verovatno.

32
00:04:33,579 --> 00:04:34,534
A Tony?

33
00:04:34,779 --> 00:04:36,974
Sigurno se raduje hotelu.

34
00:04:37,579 --> 00:04:39,855
Ne, go Torrance.

35
00:04:40,220 --> 00:04:42,495
Hajde, Tony.
Ne budi smean.

36
00:04:42,980 --> 00:04:44,778
Ne elim tamo ii.

37
00:04:45,301 --> 00:04:47,212
Kako to?

38
00:04:47,501 --> 00:04:49,298
Tako, ne elim.

39
00:04:49,701 --> 00:04:52,341
Jesu li vam neto
rekli u Denveru...

40
00:04:52,582 --> 00:04:54,140
...o prirodi posla?

41
00:04:54,382 --> 00:04:56,373
Samo u glavnim crtama.

42
00:04:58,543 --> 00:05:01,057
Zime mogu biti
strano okrutne.

43
00:05:01,303 --> 00:05:04,535
Osnovno je nositi se
s oteenjima...

44
00:05:04,784 --> 00:05:06,615
...koja uzrokuju propadanje.

45
00:05:06,864 --> 00:05:09,173
Radi se o odravanju bojlera...

46
00:05:09,424 --> 00:05:13,179
...koji naizmenino greje
delove hotela tokom dana...

47
00:05:13,425 --> 00:05:15,985
...o tekuim popravkama...

48
00:05:16,225 --> 00:05:18,899
...radi zatite od
atmosferskih uticaja.

49
00:05:19,946 --> 00:05:22,096
Zvui mi prihvatljivo.

50
00:05:22,466 --> 00:05:25,265
Fiziki, posao nije zahtevan.

51
00:05:25,507 --> 00:05:28,499
Ono to moe zimi
postati naporno...

52
00:05:28,747 --> 00:05:31,216
...je strahovit oseaj
izolovanosti.

53
00:05:32,348 --> 00:05:36,740
To je upravo ono to
mi sada treba.

54
00:05:37,109 --> 00:05:40,101
Pripremam novu knjigu.

55
00:05:40,469 --> 00:05:43,621
Pet meseci mira upravo je to
to mi treba.

56
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:46,062
Vrlo dobro, Jack.

57
00:05:46,350 --> 00:05:49,343
Jer, nekim ljudima...

58
00:05:49,591 --> 00:05:51,229
...samoa...

59
00:05:51,471 --> 00:05:52,984
...i izolacija...

60
00:05:53,831 --> 00:05:55,982
...mogu, po sebi, biti problem.

61
00:05:56,752 --> 00:05:58,344
Meni ne.

62
00:05:58,832 --> 00:06:01,870
A vaoj eni i sinu?
Hoe li oni podneti?

63
00:06:03,633 --> 00:06:04,702
Uivae.

64
00:06:04,953 --> 00:06:06,147
Odlino.

65
00:06:08,914 --> 00:06:11,986
Pre nego vas prepustim Billu...

66
00:06:12,234 --> 00:06:15,511
...ima jo neto o emu
bismo morali popriati.

67
00:06:15,755 --> 00:06:17,108
Bez dramatizovanja...

68
00:06:17,355 --> 00:06:19,744
...ali je to neke ljude...

69
00:06:19,995 --> 00:06:22,066
...odbilo od ovog posla.

70
00:06:22,756 --> 00:06:24,314
Zaintrigiran sam.

71
00:06:24,556 --> 00:06:26,751
Nisu vam nita rekli u Denveru...

72
00:06:26,996 --> 00:06:30,751
...o tragediji koju smo imali
tokom zime 1970.

73
00:06:31,357 --> 00:06:33,234
Ne verujem.

74
00:06:35,758 --> 00:06:37,350
Moj je predhodnik...

75
00:06:38,118 --> 00:06:41,191
...zaposlio Charlesa Gradya
kao uvara.

76
00:06:41,439 --> 00:06:44,715
Doao je sa enom i 2 devojice,
od 8 i 10 godina.

77
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:47,838
Bio je kompetentan,
uz dobre preporuke.

78
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:50,196
Kako su mi rekli, izgledao je...

79
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:53,000
...kao potpuno
normalna osoba.

80
00:06:53,241 --> 00:06:55,436
Ali negde tokom zime...

81
00:06:55,681 --> 00:06:59,151
...doivio je neku
vrstu nervnog sloma.

82
00:06:59,401 --> 00:07:01,597
Pomahnitao je...

83
00:07:04,882 --> 00:07:06,953
...i ubio svoju porodicu sekirom.

84
00:07:08,243 --> 00:07:12,635
Uredno ih je poslagao u sobi
zapadnog krila, i zatim...

85
00:07:13,444 --> 00:07:16,959
...sebi stavio obe cevi
puke u usta.

86
00:07:18,204 --> 00:07:19,877
Policija to pripisuje...

87
00:07:20,125 --> 00:07:23,959
...onom to su nai stari
zvali "groznica kolibe".

88
00:07:24,205 --> 00:07:27,084
Vrsta klaustrofobije
koja se moe pojaviti...

89
00:07:27,326 --> 00:07:31,285
...kad su ljudi dugo
zatvoreni zajedno.

90
00:07:36,167 --> 00:07:37,441
No, to je...

91
00:07:37,687 --> 00:07:39,121
...stvarno neobina pria.

92
00:07:40,408 --> 00:07:41,807
Da, jest.

93
00:07:42,848 --> 00:07:46,080
Neverovatno mi je
da se to stvarno desilo.

94
00:07:46,369 --> 00:07:47,961
Ali jeste.

95
00:07:49,689 --> 00:07:53,569
Razumete zato sam vam
o tome govorio.

96
00:07:54,090 --> 00:07:56,445
Svakako.

97
00:07:56,930 --> 00:07:59,399
Ali i zato su oni u Denveru...

98
00:07:59,651 --> 00:08:01,767
...to prepustili vama.

99
00:08:02,931 --> 00:08:05,492
Naravno, neke ljude
moe odbiti...

100
00:08:05,732 --> 00:08:09,611
...boravak na mestu
gde se takvo neto dogodilo.

101
00:08:09,852 --> 00:08:14,483
Moete biti sigurni da se meni
to nee dogoditi.

102
00:08:14,733 --> 00:08:18,204
A to se tie moje ene...

103
00:08:18,454 --> 00:08:22,129
...bie sigurno fascinirana
kad joj ispriam.

104
00:08:22,374 --> 00:08:25,048
Oboava prie o duhovima...

105
00:08:25,295 --> 00:08:27,570
...i filmove strave.

106
00:08:32,216 --> 00:08:35,765
Tony, misli li da e
tata dobiti posao?

107
00:08:37,137 --> 00:08:39,253
Ve je dobio.

108
00:08:39,657 --> 00:08:43,207
Uskoro e nazvati
Wendy i rei joj.

109
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:59,900
- Zdravo mala.
- Zdravo mili. Kako ide?

110
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:03,531
Odlino. U hotelu sam
i imam jo posla.

111
00:09:03,781 --> 00:09:06,693
Ne verujem da u doi
pre 9 ili 10.

112
00:09:06,941 --> 00:09:08,340
Dobio si posao.

113
00:09:08,582 --> 00:09:11,142
Tano. Mesto je predivno.

114
00:09:11,382 --> 00:09:13,373
Ti i Danny ete ga oboavati.

115
00:09:14,823 --> 00:09:17,621
Tony, zato ne eli ii u hotel?

116
00:09:17,863 --> 00:09:19,535
Ne znam.

117
00:09:20,543 --> 00:09:23,934
Zna zato.
Hajde, reci mi.

118
00:09:24,504 --> 00:09:26,495
Ne elim.

119
00:09:27,184 --> 00:09:28,379
Molim te.

120
00:09:29,545 --> 00:09:30,614
Ne.

121
00:09:30,905 --> 00:09:32,941
Hajde, Tony, reci mi.

122
00:10:01,830 --> 00:10:05,300
DAN ZATVARANJA

123
00:10:27,674 --> 00:10:31,667
Mora da smo vrlo visoko.
Vazduh je tako drugaiji.

124
00:10:37,075 --> 00:10:38,224
Tata?

125
00:10:40,956 --> 00:10:42,594
Gladan sam.

126
00:10:44,316 --> 00:10:46,956
Trebalo je da pojede doruak.

127
00:10:47,757 --> 00:10:50,510
Dobie neto
kad stignemo u hotel.

128
00:10:50,757 --> 00:10:52,316
Dobro, mama.

129
00:10:53,718 --> 00:10:57,677
Zar nije ovde negde bio zameten
Donnerov konvoj?

130
00:10:59,319 --> 00:11:02,709
Mislim da je to bilo zapadnije,
u planinama Sierra.

131
00:11:04,079 --> 00:11:06,435
ta je to Donnerov konvoj?

132
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:12,354
Kolona pokrivenih kola
s doseljenicima.

133
00:11:12,601 --> 00:11:15,673
Zimi su ostali zameteni
u planinama.

134
00:11:15,921 --> 00:11:19,961
Pribegli su kanibalizmu
da bi preiveli.

135
00:11:21,042 --> 00:11:23,796
Jeli su se meusobno?

136
00:11:24,043 --> 00:11:26,955
Morali su, da bi preiveli.

137
00:11:27,203 --> 00:11:28,352
Jack.

138
00:11:28,603 --> 00:11:29,592
Ne brini, mama.

139
00:11:29,843 --> 00:11:33,917
Znam sve o kanibalizmu.
Video sam na TV.

140
00:11:34,164 --> 00:11:36,679
Vidi, sve je u redu.

141
00:11:36,925 --> 00:11:39,200
Video je na televiziji.

142
00:12:08,689 --> 00:12:10,408
- Kad polee avion?
- U 8 i 30.

143
00:12:10,650 --> 00:12:13,244
Stii emo da sve obavimo.

144
00:12:13,490 --> 00:12:15,322
- Dovienja, g. Ullman.
- Dovienja.

145
00:12:15,571 --> 00:12:18,529
Dobro jutro.
Jeste li dugo ekali?

146
00:12:18,771 --> 00:12:21,239
Ne, ak smo i prezalogajili.

147
00:12:21,491 --> 00:12:24,211
Sreom ste stigli
pre zatvaranja kuhinje.

148
00:12:24,452 --> 00:12:26,044
Porodica vam je na obilasku?

149
00:12:26,292 --> 00:12:29,490
Ne, sin mi je otkrio
sobu za igre.

150
00:12:29,733 --> 00:12:32,645
- Uneli su vam prtljag?
- Tamo je.

151
00:12:33,213 --> 00:12:35,045
eka nas puno posla danas...

152
00:12:35,294 --> 00:12:38,764
...pa predlaem da pogledamo
va stan i ponemo.

153
00:12:39,014 --> 00:12:41,654
Odnesite stvari
u njihov stan.

154
00:12:41,895 --> 00:12:44,489
Prvo da pokupim porodicu.

155
00:12:52,256 --> 00:12:54,532
Ovo je na salon Colorado.

156
00:12:54,777 --> 00:12:57,052
Predivno.

157
00:12:57,497 --> 00:12:59,215
Moj Boe!

158
00:12:59,457 --> 00:13:01,847
Fantastino mesto,
zar ne, mili?

159
00:13:02,098 --> 00:13:03,372
Svakako.

160
00:13:54,346 --> 00:13:56,814
Ovo je krilo
za osoblje hotela.

161
00:13:57,746 --> 00:14:00,944
Druge se sobe zimi ne greju.

162
00:14:01,187 --> 00:14:03,940
- Dovienja, g. Ullman.
- Dovienja, devojke.

163
00:14:04,187 --> 00:14:06,019
A ovde je va deo.

164
00:14:06,508 --> 00:14:08,942
Dnevna soba,
spavaa soba, kupatilo.

165
00:14:09,188 --> 00:14:11,623
I mala soba za vaeg sina.

166
00:14:15,029 --> 00:14:16,985
Savreno za dete.

167
00:14:25,031 --> 00:14:27,067
Kad je sagraen Vidikovac?

168
00:14:28,031 --> 00:14:30,147
Gradnja je zapoela 1907.

169
00:14:30,391 --> 00:14:32,223
Zavrena je 1909.

170
00:14:32,472 --> 00:14:34,940
Tu je bilo indijansko groblje.

171
00:14:35,192 --> 00:14:39,789
Odbili su par indijanskih napada
za vreme gradnje.

172
00:14:40,313 --> 00:14:42,144
Ovo je na Ratrak.

173
00:14:42,793 --> 00:14:44,750
Oboje vozite?

174
00:14:45,274 --> 00:14:48,710
Dobro. Ratrak funkcionira
vrlo slino autu.

175
00:14:48,954 --> 00:14:50,547
Naviknuete se brzo.

176
00:14:51,275 --> 00:14:52,788
Ovo je kuhinja?

177
00:14:53,035 --> 00:14:54,514
Tako je.

178
00:14:54,755 --> 00:14:57,589
Kako ti se svia, Danny?
Dovoljno ti je velika?

179
00:14:58,396 --> 00:15:00,512
Nikad nisam video veu.

180
00:15:00,756 --> 00:15:02,907
Ovo je mesto ogromni lavirint.

181
00:15:03,157 --> 00:15:06,832
Morau bacati mrvice
kad god doem.

182
00:15:07,477 --> 00:15:09,196
Samo hrabro.

183
00:15:09,438 --> 00:15:11,747
Velika je, ali ipak je
samo kuhinja.

184
00:15:11,998 --> 00:15:14,068
Veinom stvari se
neete ni sluiti.

185
00:15:14,318 --> 00:15:16,435
Ne bih ni znala kako.

186
00:15:16,679 --> 00:15:19,591
Jedno je sigurno.
Ne morate brinuti o hrani.

187
00:15:19,839 --> 00:15:24,277
U godinu dana ne biste imali
dvaput isti jelovnik.

188
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:27,432
Ovde je naa hladnjaa.

189
00:15:28,601 --> 00:15:31,479
Ovde drimo nae meso.

190
00:15:31,721 --> 00:15:33,552
Imate 15 komada pleki...

191
00:15:33,801 --> 00:15:35,793
...30 vrea hamburgera.

192
00:15:36,042 --> 00:15:38,920
Imamo 12 urki,
oko 40 kokoaka...

193
00:15:39,162 --> 00:15:42,121
...50 odrezaka, dva tuceta
svinjskih peenica...

194
00:15:42,363 --> 00:15:45,196
...i 20 jagnjeih butova.
Voli jagnjetinu, efe?

195
00:15:46,403 --> 00:15:48,634
Ne? Koje ti je najdrae jelo?

196
00:15:48,884 --> 00:15:50,681
Pomfrit s keapom.

197
00:15:51,364 --> 00:15:53,241
Sredit emo to, efe.

198
00:15:53,484 --> 00:15:55,043
Doi. Pazi kamo staje.

199
00:16:01,486 --> 00:16:03,044
Kako znate za "efe"?

200
00:16:03,286 --> 00:16:07,120
- Oprostite?
- Dvaput ste ga nazvali "efe".

201
00:16:07,367 --> 00:16:08,686
Jesam li?

202
00:16:09,487 --> 00:16:12,445
Zovemo ga "efe", kao u
crtanima sa Dukom Dugoukom.

203
00:16:12,687 --> 00:16:13,803
Ali kako ste vi to znali?

204
00:16:14,048 --> 00:16:16,482
Moda sam uo od vas.

205
00:16:16,728 --> 00:16:18,844
Mogue.
Ali se ne seam...

206
00:16:19,088 --> 00:16:21,159
...da sam ga sad tako zvala.

207
00:16:21,409 --> 00:16:23,445
Izgleda kao ef, zar ne?

208
00:16:24,849 --> 00:16:26,202
efe, koji ti je vrag?

209
00:16:27,970 --> 00:16:30,086
Evo i ostave.

210
00:16:31,770 --> 00:16:36,401
Ovde drimo suene namirnice
i konzerve.

211
00:16:36,651 --> 00:16:38,881
Imamo konzervirano
voe i povre...

212
00:16:39,131 --> 00:16:42,727
...konzervirane ribe i meso,
sve vrste itarica.

213
00:16:42,972 --> 00:16:45,965
Tostove, kukuruzne,
slatke, zobene...

214
00:16:46,213 --> 00:16:50,047
...i pirinane pahuljice,
kreme od pirina i od penice.

215
00:16:50,293 --> 00:16:52,569
Imamo 12 tegli slada.

216
00:16:52,814 --> 00:16:55,851
60 kutija mleka u prahu...

217
00:17:03,175 --> 00:17:05,531
Voli sladoled, efe?

218
00:17:07,856 --> 00:17:09,733
...grickalice, kekse...

219
00:17:10,016 --> 00:17:11,369
...i 7 vrsta svega i svaega.

220
00:17:11,617 --> 00:17:14,973
Imamo suvih breskvi,
suvih marelica...

221
00:17:15,217 --> 00:17:18,130
...suvog groa i suvih ljiva.

222
00:17:18,458 --> 00:17:22,531
Morate imati urednu probavu
da biste bili sreni.

223
00:17:25,339 --> 00:17:26,818
- Kako ide?
- Dobro.

224
00:17:27,059 --> 00:17:30,449
Posudite nam gu Torrance.
Kreemo u podrum.

225
00:17:30,699 --> 00:17:32,452
Neemo je dugo zadrati.

226
00:17:32,700 --> 00:17:35,737
U redu. Upravo sam
stigao do sladoleda.

227
00:17:35,980 --> 00:17:37,778
Voli sladoled, efe?

228
00:17:38,541 --> 00:17:39,496
Tako sam i mislio.

229
00:17:39,741 --> 00:17:42,619
Mogu li Dannyu
dati malo sladoleda?

230
00:17:42,861 --> 00:17:44,580
- Naravno.
- Moete.

231
00:17:44,822 --> 00:17:46,858
- Dobro.
- ta ti misli, efe?

232
00:17:47,102 --> 00:17:49,093
Dobro, budi dobar.

233
00:17:51,983 --> 00:17:53,735
Kakav sladoled voli?

234
00:17:53,983 --> 00:17:54,779
okoladni.

235
00:17:55,023 --> 00:17:57,857
I bie okoladni.
Doi, sinko.

236
00:18:02,304 --> 00:18:04,136
udno, koliko aktivnosti.

237
00:18:04,385 --> 00:18:07,024
Gosti i deo osoblja
su otili jue, ali...

238
00:18:07,265 --> 00:18:08,618
...poslednji je dan ludnica.

